 kdelibs5-dev (>= 4:4.3.4), kdebase-workspace-dev(>= 4:4.3.4), libx11-dev
Homepage: http://www.kde-look.org/content/show.php?content=40492
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/tehnick/kde-style-qtcurve-debian.git
